cross: Sarcochilus Kulnura Sanctuary x Sarcochilus Kulnura Gifted

measurements.description: Twenty-four flowers and two buds on four upright infloresences up to 14cm long; sepals and petals overlapping, generally flat, depressed centrally, white speckled uniformly dusty mauve; lip white, marked gold distally, side lobes striped purple; column white, anther cap white; substance firm; texture crystalline.
